                "body": "<p>I hope someone else finds these as clever as I did.</p>\n<p>Board game (5) - DARTS</p>\n<p>Ear borrower (6) - ANTONY</p>\n<p>Sink alternative (4) - SWIM</p>\n<p>Keys on the piano (6) - ALICIA</p>\n<p>Family member (5) - GENUS</p>\n<p>One in charge of late admissions (7) - STPETER</p>\n<p>One noted for bringing couples together (4) - NOAH</p>\n<p>Announce retirement (8) - PLAYTAPS</p>\n<p>Q7 and R8, e.g. (5) - AUDIS</p>\n<p>Venus’s lack (4) - ARMS (MOON was acceptable but not as clever)</p>\n<p>Bond rating (7) - VALENCE</p>\n<p>More than fast (6) - STARVE</p>\n<p>What some waiters never see (5) - GODOT</p>\n<p>Highest livestock bidder (15) - RICHARDTHETHIRD</p>",
