                "note_count": 1,
                "title": "Average Friday",
                "body": "<p>Here&rsquo;s a typical Friday in Kevin&rsquo;s Fa13 semester.</p>\n<p>Four classes with homework due: A at 4 pm, B at 6pm, C at 4pm</p>\n<ul><li>12:00: Homework for class A</li>\n<li>12:30: Power nap</li>\n<li>1:00: Wake up</li>\n<li>1:30: Another power nap</li>\n<li>1:45: Change alarm to 2:00</li>\n<li>2:00: Change alarm to 3:00</li>\n<li>3:00: Decide to sleep</li>\n<li>6:30: Wake up, try to do homework A</li>\n<li>6:35: Fall asleep</li>\n<li>9:00: Wake up, shower, eat breakfast </li>\n<li>10:00: Get to class late</li>\n<li>11:00: Skip class to do homework B</li>\n<li>12:00: Lunch, decide to not do homework A</li>\n<li>1:00: Go to class C, start homework C</li>\n<li>2:00: Go to class D, continue homework C</li>\n<li>3:00: Skip class A, finish homework C</li>\n<li>4:00: Turn in homework C, continue homework B</li>\n<li>5:00: Continue homework B.</li>\n<li>6:00 to 12:00: ?????</li>\n</ul><p>This note was published at 5:09 pm, so I&rsquo;m actually still working on homework B.</p>",
